flowgate (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Expand OS detection to support 30+ Linux distributions.
  * Add OS family mapping (debian, rhel, arch, alpine, suse, gentoo, void, freebsd).
  * Show install commands only for missing packages in doctor output.
  * Add universal init system support (systemd, openrc, sysvinit, runit, s6).
  * Auto-detect nginx user (www-data, nginx, http, wwwrun) for config files.
  * Rename FlowWeb to Flowgate Web consistently.
  * Fix Makefile install-web target for file installation.
  * Update .gitignore to exclude Debian build artifacts.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Mon, 06 Jan 2026 17:15:06 +0300

